OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny
OL,6,Fremaining heavy showers will gradually
OL,7,Fease and clear eastwards, leaving a
OL,8,Flargely dry night with occasional
OL,9,Fclear spells. However, the odd spot of
OL,10,Frain remains possible, particularly in
OL,11,Fthe west. Mild and breezy throughout.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FIncreasingly cloudy, ahead
OL,14,Fof a band of rain sweeping east across
OL,15,Fthe region. Sunny spells and blustery
OL,16,Fshowers developing in the afternoon,
OL,17,Fheavy in places. Showers easing in the
OL,18,Fevening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
